headline: Fed decision, DraftKings, mortgage rates: What to Watch
summary: The Federal Reserve will conclude its November FOMC meeting tomorrow — Wednesday, November 7 — announcing its latest interest rate decision, followed by a press conference with Fed Chair Jerome Powell. The companies scheduled to release their latest earnings results include Airbnb (ABNB), DraftKings (DKNG), Moderna (MRNA), and Warner Bros. Discovery (WBD). Lastly, the weekly mortgage rate reading is also due out tomorrow. The 30-year fixed rate mortgage average sits at 6.72%. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Asking for a Trend here. This post was written by Luke Carberry Mogan.
